                                                                                                                        【安排！南京<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%8E%84%E6%AD%A6%E6%B9%96%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA%E8%AF%B7%E5%89%8D%E7%BA%BF%E5%8C%BB%E6%8A%A4%E5%9D%90%E9%B8%AD%E5%AD%90%E8%88%B9%23&amp;from=default">#玄武湖景区请前线医护坐鸭子船#</a><img class="W_img_face" render="ext" src="//img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/71/2018new_touxiao_org.png" title="[偷笑]" alt="[偷笑]" type="face" style="visibility: hidden;">】近日，<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E9%BC%93%E6%A5%BC%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=南京鼓楼医院">@南京鼓楼医院</a> 五位支援武汉的医护人员，在防护服贴上玄武湖、中山陵等南京地标景点。听到医护人员的心声，<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%84%E6%AD%A6%E6%B9%96?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=南京市玄武湖">@南京市玄武湖</a> 立刻安排上了：所有勇士，回来免费请你们坐鸭子船！盼望前线勇士早日凯旋。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E8%8D%94%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=荔直播">@荔直播</a> <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4476345557822111:2017607-video:2017607%3A4476321158332435:page_100206_home:2286908003:4476345557822111:2286908003" title="荔直播的秒拍视频" href="http://t.cn/A67wyZ3u" alt="http://t.cn/A67wyZ3u" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>荔直播的秒拍视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

        <!-- 如果返回的为空，但是有二级评论 -->
        <!-- 如果返回有二级评论 -->
        <!-- 为评论假写留下二级评论的样式框架评论 -->
                <div class="list_box_in S_bg3" style="display:none">
            <div class="list_ul" node-type="child_comment">
            <div class="between_line S_bg1"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
                        <!-- 为评论假写留下二级评论的样式框架评论 -->
                 <!-- 如果返回有二级评论 -->
        <!-- 二级评论 -->
        <!-- 对一级评论的操作 -->
    </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E8%80%81%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%BF%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%8D%87%E6%97%97%23&amp;from=default">#老校长在线直播升旗#</a> 2万学生观看】近日，原本是<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%AC%E5%AD%A6%E9%99%A2?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=西京学院">@西京学院</a> 春季学期开学的日子，受疫情影响，学生们没有返校。为了新学期第一次升旗仪式能正常进行，学校举行了一次特别的线上升旗仪式。学生们在家中通过网络观看升旗视频。学校董事长、老校长任万钧担当升旗手，将五星红旗冉冉升起。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%8E%85?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=陕西省教育厅">@陕西省教育厅</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【世卫组织：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E6%97%A5%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E9%A6%96%E8%B6%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A2%83%E5%86%85%23&amp;from=default">#境外日新增病例首超中国境内#</a>】当地时间26日，世卫组织总干事谭德塞在日内瓦表示，25日中国境外上报的新冠肺炎新增病例数首次超过中国新增病例数，目前意大利、伊朗、韩国的情况令人十分担忧。（央视） ​​​​                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476315359429684" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw1jhDz5G?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 20:30" date="1582720210000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476315359429684:fromprofile"> 2月26日 20:30</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/2O2xZO" rel="nofollow">人民网微博</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%8E%A8%E5%B8%88%E8%A2%AB%E8%AF%AF%E8%A7%A3%E5%A7%94%E5%B1%88%E8%90%BD%E6%B3%AA%23&amp;from=default">#六旬厨师被误解委屈落泪#</a>】因另一位厨师被隔离，60多岁的潘师傅从春节前一直加班，每天为60多位民警提供一日三餐，买菜、洗菜、做厨房保洁。因工作没得到同事的认可，觉得自己好心没被理解而落泪。在民警安慰下潘师傅逐渐平复情绪，继续投入工作。致敬每个努力坚持的劳动者！<a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4476315359429684:1034-video:1034%3A4476266984964114:page_100206_home:2286908003:4476315359429684:2286908003" title="侠客岛的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A67Zie3c" alt="http://t.cn/A67Zie3c" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>侠客岛的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                 <!-- 如果返回有二级评论 -->

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609309125&amp;ssig=Y%2BmZQTeNT9" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

        <div class="WB_detail">

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476307058650405" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw15TAimF?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 19:57" date="1582718231000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476307058650405:fromprofile"> 2月26日 19:57</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6ghA0p" rel="nofollow">搜狗高速浏览器</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【国际奥委会：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A5%E8%BF%90%E6%8C%89%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9B%23&amp;from=default">#东京奥运按计划推进#</a> 其他言论均属猜测】针对国际奥委会委员迪克·庞德做出的“如果三个月之后新冠肺炎疫情威胁不能消除，2020年东京奥运会可能取消”的判断，国际奥委会发言人26日表示，国际奥委会正为东京2020年奥运会如期成功举办而不断努力，庞德的言论很好地解释了这一点。除此之外 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Iw15TAimF" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476307058650405:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476307058650405&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609309125&amp;ssig=Y%2BmZQTeNT9" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>
                    </div>

        <div class="WB_detail">
                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476303795177616" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw10DlIVW?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 19:44" date="1582717453000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476303795177616:fromprofile"> 2月26日 19:44</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/2O2xZO" rel="nofollow">人民网微博</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E7%8E%B0%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%23&amp;from=default">#希腊现首例新冠肺炎患者#</a>】当地时间2月26日，希腊卫生部门宣布，在希腊北部第一大城市塞萨洛尼基，出现希腊第一例新型冠状病毒感染者。该患者为38岁希腊女性，近期曾前往意大利旅行。（央视） ​​​​                                            </div>

</div>

        <div class="WB_detail">

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>

                                <a name="4476300259229078" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw0UVCIU6?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 19:30" date="1582716610000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476300259229078:fromprofile"> 2月26日 19:30</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/2O2xZO" rel="nofollow">人民网微博</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%89%B9%E6%95%99%E8%80%81%E5%B8%88%E5%BD%95%E6%89%8B%E8%AF%AD%E7%BD%91%E8%AF%BE%E8%BE%85%E5%AF%BC%E8%81%8B%E5%93%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%23&amp;from=default">#特教老师录手语网课辅导聋哑学生#</a>】吴耀宇是扬州特殊教育学校的数学老师，学生都是聋哑人。疫情期间，他用手语精心录制解题视频，通过视频连线追踪学生的学习情况。吴耀宇也是聋哑人，他的父亲曾写下上万张字条为他鼓劲。如今，他希望把这份勇气传给每一个学生。<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E8%8D%94%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=荔直播">@荔直播</a> <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4476300259229078:2017607-video:2017607%3A4476273343528996:page_100206_home:2286908003:4476300259229078:2286908003" title="荔直播的秒拍视频" href="http://t.cn/A67ZKuRc" alt="http://t.cn/A67ZKuRc" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>荔直播的秒拍视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476295495030697" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw0Nfl6Ih?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 19:11" date="1582715474000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476295495030697:fromprofile"> 2月26日 19:11</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6ghA0p" rel="nofollow">搜狗高速浏览器</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【中组部：在抗疫一线事迹突出的入党积极分子可“火线”入党】近日，中央领导同志作出重要指示，在新冠肺炎疫情防控斗争中，对那些在抗疫一线事迹突出的入党积极分子，可根据其表现“火线”发展入党。为贯彻落实中央领导同志重要指示精神，中央组织部印发通知，要求各级党组织抓紧做好在抗疫一线发展党 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Iw0Nfl6Ih" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476295495030697:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476295495030697&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476294596936139" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Iw0LNt6pd?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 19:07" date="1582715260000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476294596936139:fromprofile"> 2月26日 19:07</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【习近平主持召开中共中央政治局常务委员会会议】中共中央政治局常务委员会2月26日召开会议，听取中央应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情工作领导小组汇报，分析当前疫情形势，研究部署近期防控重点工作。中共中央总书记习近平主持会议并发表重要讲话。<br>响应党中央对广大党员的号召，习近平、李克强、栗战书 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Iw0LNt6pd" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476294596936139:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476294596936139&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%A8N95%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%A7%E8%83%BD107%E4%B8%87%E5%8F%AA%23&amp;from=default">#医用N95口罩日产能107万只#</a>】截至2月24日，全国医用N95口罩日产能达到107万只，是2月1日的4.7倍。2月1日至25日，累计向湖北调运医用N95口罩304万只，近期每天的调度量都在15万只以上，加上湖北省内的生产，有效保障了一线医护人员的防护需要。<a suda-uatrack="key=minicard&amp;value=pagelink_minicard_click" title="网页链接" href="http://t.cn/A67Z0c2Z" alt="http://t.cn/A67Z0c2Z" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_link">O</i>网页链接</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                        <a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/ssill1007" usercard="id=1353284612">未弈</a>：微量的沐浴露擦眼镜自然风干也可以防雾，防雾湿巾镜布好像就是这个原理，不过天太冷的时候需要频繁擦拭，因水汽大也会看不清                    </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【致敬！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%80%80%E4%BC%8D%E5%86%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%93%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%92%E5%91%98%23&amp;from=default">#退伍军人当病毒样本快递员#</a>】46岁的退伍军人刘森波是一名“病毒样本快递员”。2月19日，他从广州来到武汉支援抗疫工作，并主动请缨承担高风险任务——武汉雷神山医院样本物流收取和运送工作。刘森波每日要跑两趟到武汉雷神山医院收取样本，并在半小时内送到核酸检测服务机构。（新华社） ​​​​                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609309137&amp;ssig=A4L0%2FwcRbe" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

        <div class="WB_detail">
                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476259852062581" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IvZRL8Ezr?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 16:49" date="1582706976000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476259852062581:fromprofile"> 2月26日 16:49</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【出舱！武汉<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%BB%E6%96%B9%E8%88%B1%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%87%BA%E9%99%A2%23&amp;from=default">#首个中医方舱医院首批患者出院#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>26日上午，武汉首个中医方舱医院迎来首批病人出院。首批出院的23人中，最小的27岁，最大的56岁。根据各人身体状况，中医专家还为他们开了出院后的个性化康复药方。出院后，23人都被各区派车接到指定隔离点，进行为期14天的观察，之后再 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZRL8Ezr" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476259852062581:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476259852062581&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%A9%B4%E5%84%BF%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%23&amp;from=default">#如何做好婴儿疫情防护措施#</a>？】中国疾控中心研究员冯录召介绍：婴儿的防护主要以被动防护为主，为尽可能降低婴儿感染的风险，可<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%9C%8B%E6%8A%A4%E4%BA%BA%E7%85%A7%E7%9C%8B%E5%A9%B4%E5%84%BF%23&amp;from=default">#相对固定一个看护人照看婴儿#</a>，看护人尽量不外出。要戴好口罩，不要对着孩子打喷嚏、呼气；接触儿童玩具、用具或生活用品之前，以及交流玩耍之前，都要清洗双手。不要共 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZJKmfJl" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476254885303687:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476254885303687&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%B7%B2%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B40%E4%BD%99%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%BD%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%23&amp;from=default">#餐饮企业已免费提供40余万份餐饮#</a>】<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>商务部服贸司司长冼国义：一些生活服务企业、电商平台，积极为抗疫一线提供服务保障，有的还是免费。据不完全统计，截至到2月中旬，餐饮住宿企业共为武汉等地一线抗疫人员免费提供40余万份餐饮，1万余间房间。 <a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4476254793272885:1042163-video:1042163%3A4476254695391241:page_100206_home:2286908003:4476254793272885:2286908003" title="人民网的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A67ZUKJ7" alt="http://t.cn/A67ZUKJ7" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>人民网的微博视频</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【770座滑雪场客流量断崖式下滑】用3个对比来描述冰雪产业运营情况：①最好的雪季与最短的营业，1月24日各地滑雪场陆续关闭，大大压缩了运营时间；②最多的滑雪场与最少的客流量，<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23770%E5%BA%A7%E6%BB%91%E9%9B%AA%E5%9C%BA%E5%AE%A2%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E6%96%AD%E5%B4%96%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91%23&amp;from=default">#770座滑雪场客流量断崖式下滑#</a>，河北的滑雪场接待人数较2019年下滑278万人次；③最充分的准备与最差的市场表现。&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZF1dXxW" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476251953327164:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476251953327164&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609309142&amp;ssig=7Rv5d%2FlqMb" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>
                    </div>

        <div class="WB_detail">
                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476250783850829" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IvZD8g9M9?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 16:13" date="1582704813000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476250783850829:fromprofile"> 2月26日 16:13</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/4iDt6Q" rel="nofollow">微博云剪</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>
                                                </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【文旅部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%BB%9E%E7%95%99%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%98%E5%89%A9%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B090%E4%BA%BA%23&amp;from=default">#滞留海外团队游客还剩不到90人#</a>】文化和旅游部市场管理司司长刘克智表示：据统计，从1月24日开始，暂停经营团队旅游业务以后，当时在海外团队游客达25万。在外交、民航部门的大力支持下，通过包机、改签航班，陆续有序返回。 <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%97%A0%E8%AE%BA%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E8%BF%9C%E6%96%B9%E7%A5%96%E5%9B%BD%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%A0%E8%BA%AB%E5%90%8E%23&amp;from=default">#无论你在哪个远方祖国始终在你身后#</a>，截至25日，还剩下不到90人 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZD8g9M9" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476250783850829:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476250783850829&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD%E7%B4%AF%E8%AE%A1%E7%A1%AE%E8%AF%8A1261%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#韩国累计确诊1261例#</a>，一天增加284例】韩国中央防疫对策本部26日通报，截至当地时间当天下午4时，韩国较当天上午9时新增115例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计确诊病例达1261例，共出现12例死亡病例。与前一天下午4时相比，一天内增加病例284例。韩联社报道称，韩国将于明日起每天通过药店 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZCW5WPi" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476250661417772:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476250661417772&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%9613%E4%B8%87%E5%8D%95%23&amp;from=default">#武汉一天外卖13万单#</a>】目前餐饮住宿业都在逐步复工，企业收入有所回升。20家大型连锁餐饮企业复工率达57%，住宿业复工率达50%以上。业态不同，复工方式也不一样。餐饮业复工主要以外卖方式，武汉昨天一天餐饮外卖13万单。低风险地区住宿、餐饮堂食也在复工，要做好防护，分散就餐。&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZxfBq06" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476247138918086:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476247138918086&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4476245310169506" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IvZuj0I5Y?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-26 15:51" date="1582703509000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4476245310169506:fromprofile"> 2月26日 15:51</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/4iDt6Q" rel="nofollow">微博云剪</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E6%90%9E%E4%B8%80%E5%88%80%E5%88%87%23&amp;from=default">#旅游景区开放不宜搞一刀切#</a> <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%AB%98%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA%E6%9A%82%E7%BC%93%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%23&amp;from=default">#疫情高风险地区旅游景区暂缓开放#</a>】旅游景区具有“人员聚集性强，人员流动性大”的特点，旅游景区的恢复开放，应当坚持分区分级的原则，对旅游景区开放的条件和必要性进行评估，不宜搞一刀切。疫情高风险地区旅游景区暂缓开放，中风险低风险地区旅游景区由当地党委政府 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZuj0I5Y" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476245310169506:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476245310169506&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【受疫情影响 <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%AF%B9%E6%96%87%E6%97%85%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E5%85%8D%E5%BE%81%E5%A2%9E%E5%80%BC%E7%A8%8E%23&amp;from=default">#对文旅等服务取得的收入免征增值税#</a>】2月5日，决定向旅行社暂退部分旅游服务保证金，暂退的范围是全国已缴纳保证金、领取旅行社经营许可证的旅行社，暂退的标准为 80%。截止25日，应该退保证金总额为80亿，已经退还34.62亿元，有效缓解了企业现金流压力。为文旅企业纾困解难：①推动涉及 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IvZqt8W7D" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4476242932130049:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4476242932130049&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                 【<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" suda-uatrack=\"key=topic_click&value=click_topic\" class=\"a_topic\" extra-data=\"type=topic\" href=\"\/\/s.weibo.com\/weibo?q=%23%E8%80%81%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%BF%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%8D%87%E6%97%97%23&from=default\">#老校长在线直播升旗#<\/a> 2万学生观看】近日，原本是<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" extra-data=\"type=atname\" href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/n\/%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%AC%E5%AD%A6%E9%99%A2?from=feed&loc=at\" usercard=\"name=西京学院\">@西京学院<\/a> 春季学期开学的日子，受疫情影响，学生们没有返校。为了新学期第一次升旗仪式能正常进行，学校举行了一次特别的线上升旗仪式。学生们在家中通过网络观看升旗视频。学校董事长、老校长任万钧担当升旗手，将五星红旗冉冉升起。<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" extra-data=\"type=atname\"
